c\n        sSup S ≤ sSup (decomposition_of_refinement R) := sSup_le (by\n          intro x hx\n          -- If x is in S, then it is in the decomposition\n          have h₃ : x ∈ decomposition_of_refinement R := h₂ hx\n          exact h₃)\n        _ = sSup (decomposition_of_refinement R) := by rfl\n  exact h₁",
